Developed comprehensive data mapping, records retention and eDiscovery governance policies for major telecommunications company.
    
Represented global pharmaceutical company in developing eDiscovery governance policies and procedures in domestic and European operations.
    
Advised national specialty retailer on retention, preservation and collection issues for structured and unstructured ESI in response to multiple government investigations.
    








Insurance, Mass Tort & Labor Litigation





